{"tid":1022631,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[帶風向的台媒] ITZY太火 粉絲擔心「她」！Somi反過來安慰","createTime":"2019-02-15T07:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T11:48:15.000Z","uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6d06183f970ad1beae4e94df3b27e9a131fd1f42","tid":1022631,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T07:00:22.000Z","msg":"ITZY太火粉絲擔心「她」！Somi反過來安慰<br />\n<br />\n女團TWICE終於有師妹團，JYP娛樂新生代女團ITZY昨（12）日正式出道，從MV點閱到音源排行都氣勢驚人，ITZY火紅卻讓粉絲擔心從JYP出走的Somi（全昭彌）心情受到影響，<strong>她也用韓英文雙語在IG上回應「是我太貪心了」(????)</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n眼看JYP都推出新女團ITZY，且一出道成績不俗，MV點閱僅一天就破千萬，新歌《달라달라(DALLA DALLA)》更是通殺音源榜單冠軍，反觀Somi與夯團再度擦身而過，到現在也還沒發片消息，讓粉絲十分擔心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3893/d3893669.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3893%2Fd3893669.jpg&h=16b321f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲Somi以雙語安慰粉絲，坦言：是我太貪心了。（圖／翻攝自Somi IG）<br />\n<br />\nSomi也在IG上以韓語跟英文回應了，「給我親愛的粉絲，不要覺得我很遙遠，也不要難過或是失落地等待著我。因為我並沒有和你們距離很遠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真的，那天會到來的！我希望大家能非常興奮期待！別誤會我，<strong>『因為我要求一切完美』</strong>，所以其實是因為我<strong>『太過分貪心了』</strong>。」最後希望大家能期待她的作品，貼心反過來安慰粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台媒世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f061da4e0c9c6cce940965ca65b86f896714c47f","tid":1022631,"uid":171598,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T07:02:51.000Z","msg":"琴日先有人貼完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf967307634565a0afb90a1f63ccd7d99bd3c983","tid":1022631,"uid":74065,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"f061da4e0c9c6cce940965ca65b86f896714c47f","tid":1022631,"uid":171598,"like":3,"dislik